sample_data.proc_sql:
SELECT DISTINCT
			   trig.osgb_gridref
		     , trig.physical_type
			 , coalesce(logu.user_id = 18, 0) as log_user
			 , count(distinct(logo.id)) as log_count
		FROM trig
			 left outer join log logu on trig.id = logu.trig_id and logu.user_id = 18
			 left outer join log logo on trig.id = logo.trig_id
		 
		GROUP BY trig.osgb_gridref
		       , trig.physical_type
			   , log_user
		ORDER BY pow(trig.osgb_eastings - 518651,2) + pow(trig.osgb_northings - 173160,2)
		LIMIT 0,10
